node.text: Thanks for this beautiful video of our first day at @fspuntamita for Nathan’s birthday @burnt_recordings 🌴 🌊

Bienvenidos a Costa Rica! Cheers to an adventure of a lifetime. A huge thank you to @whotelscostarica for having me! See the full video on my YouTube channel 🙏⁣

node.text: Join Julien’s Auctions on Friday, November 30th and Saturday, December 1st in Los Angeles and live online at Julien's Live for our "Property From The Collection of Hugh M. Hefner" auction as we celebrate the pop culture icon and publishing giant who introduced the world to the legendary Playboy brand. All proceeds of the sale will benefit The Hugh M. Hefner Foundation in support of organizations that advocate for and defend civil rights, with special emphasis on First Amendment rights and rational sex and drug policies since 1964.

node.title: Julien’s Auctions: Property From The Collection of Hugh M. Hefner

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Crystal Hefner in Santa Monica, California with @crystalhefner, @raeraeftz, @bethdoane, @noellecors, @oceanasantamonica, @long_qt_syndrome, and @longqt_cyclist. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
I’ve been surrounding myself with people I love and trying to take things easy lately. I’m healing from things in my life and growing as a person. On top of the health related things I’m still healing from, I was recently diagnosed with a rare heart rhythm disorder called “long qt” syndrome. I’ve been lucky to find people on social media who have it as well and they’ve helped me tremendously. For those who have it, you are not alone. As I try and simplify my life even more and learn about my diagnosis, I’ve found it best to just focus on myself lately. I recently ended a year long relationship and am just trying to get myself to a place of happiness and wellness. I love you all so much and I appreciate those of you who have followed my journey and different paths. So much love to you. ❤️ Crystal ⁣
⁣
#longqt #lyme #bii #life #lqts #health #autoimmune #wellness #love #calm #oceanasantamonica #oceana #crystalhefner ⁣
⁣
📸 @bethdoane⁣
🏡 @oceanasantamonica
